{{vgname|画中世界|en=Gorogoa|cn=画中世界|tw=圖中畫}}是一款[[益智游戏|解谜类]][[电子游戏|电子游戏]]，由杰森·罗伯茨开发，[[安纳布尔纳互动|安纳布尔纳互动]]发行。游戏于2017年12月14日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]和[[iOS|iOS]]平台发行，2018年3月登陆[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]，不久后上架[[Android|Android]]和[[Kindle_Fire|Kindle Fire]]平台<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.androidauthority.com/gorogoa-android-877592/|title=Gorgeous award-winning puzzler Gorogoa up for pre-registration on Play Store|last=Cragg|first=Oliver|date=2018-06-19|website=Android Authority|access-date=2018-07-02|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702122126/https://www.androidauthority.com/gorogoa-android-877592/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏由罗伯茨一人独立开发，最开始他想把游戏打造成互动式图画小说，但没有成功，后来历时近六年才完成这部作品。

玩家在游戏中须操纵置于2×2方格中的四幅图画，探索每幅图画中的环境，通过叠放图画或调整图画次序的方式解决谜题。谜题中，玩家须指引主角小男孩在饱受战争摧残的家园中对付一个奇怪的怪物，重建世界。游戏末尾，小男孩渐渐长大，最终变成老人，回忆起自己的过往。

== 游戏玩法 ==
[[File:Gorogoa-gameplay.gif|thumb]]
游戏中，玩家会接触到置于2×2方格的四幅图画。这些图画多数会自动放大缩小或平移，但玩家仍需将其中一些图画移至其他方格空间。部分图画会带有门口之类空缺的地方，玩家将其移动到其他图画时，这些图画会遮盖住现有的图画，从而形成新的图画。因此，玩家必须堆叠、组合、探索每一张图画，才能找出每幅图画之间的关联，推动游戏发展，开启新空间<ref name="Polygon">{{cite web |url= http://www.polygon.com/2013/5/25/4363936/gorogoa-puzzle-in-the-picture |title= Puzzle in the picture: how Gorogoa brings art to life through mind-twisting challenges |date= 2013-05-25 |accessdate= 2014-01-02 |first= Megan |last= Farokhmanesh |work= Polygon |archive-date= 2019-03-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190309025119/https://www.polygon.com/2013/5/25/4363936/gorogoa-puzzle-in-the-picture |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/10/12/windows-2013-gorogoa/ |title= Windows 2013: Gorogoa |date= 2012-10-12 |accessdate= 2013-01-02 |work= Rock, Paper, Shotgun |first= Alec |last= Meer |archive-date= 2019-04-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190419122758/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/10/12/windows-2013-gorogoa/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。在这种过程中，由于游戏没有任何对白或字幕提示，玩家不会获得提示，必须自行找出完成每一关的方法。不过玩家成功完成关卡时，画面会自行活动，向玩家展示成功找出画面间关系后的结果<ref name="Kotaku">{{cite web |url= http://kotaku.com/5960433/if-you-like-comics-or-trippy-dreams-youll-love-this-game |title= If You Like Comics Or Trippy Dreams, You'll Love This Game |date= 2012-11-14 |accessdate= 2014-01-02 |first= Patricia |last= Hernandez |work= Kotaku |archive-date= 2018-11-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181122210100/https://kotaku.com/5960433/if-you-like-comics-or-trippy-dreams-youll-love-this-game |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/12/04/hands-on-gorogoa-a-puzzle-game-about-pictures/ |title= Hands On: Gorogoa, A Puzzle Game About Pictures |date= 2013-12-04 |accessdate= 2014-01-02 |first= Graham |last= Smith |work= Rock, Paper, Shotgun |archive-date= 2020-11-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201126154625/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/12/04/hands-on-gorogoa-a-puzzle-game-about-pictures/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

游戏讲述了一个小男孩和一位神兽之间的故事，探讨[[靈性|靈性]]和[[宗教|宗教]]两大主题<ref name="Kotaku"/><ref name="EuroG">{{cite web |url= http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-11-brilliant-hand-illustrated-indie-puzzler-gorogoa-now-has-a-demo |title= Brilliant hand-illustrated Indiecade finalist Gorogoa now has a demo |date= 2012-10-11 |first= Jeffrey |last= Matulef |work= Eurogamer |accessdate= 2021-02-24 |archive-date= 2020-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200303112532/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-11-brilliant-hand-illustrated-indie-puzzler-gorogoa-now-has-a-demo |dead-url= no }}</ref>。背景则设置在20世纪，通篇都是战争与和平、战后重建的景象，而主人公小男孩也是战争的幸存者，后半生亲身经历家园重建的过程，最终变成老人，蓦然回首往事<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=https://kotaku.com/the-puzzle-of-a-lifetime-1821235999|title=The Puzzle Of A Lifetime|last=Kohler|first=Chris|date=2017-12-14|work=Kotaku|access-date=2017-12-23|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204060616/https://kotaku.com/the-puzzle-of-a-lifetime-1821235999|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.avclub.com/gorogoa-wants-to-get-you-thinking-about-much-more-than-1821949817 | title = Gorogoa wants to get you thinking about much more than its breathtaking puzzles | first = Matt | last = Geraldi | date = 2018-01-11 | accessdate = 2018-11-07 | work = The A.V. Club | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127154941/https://www.avclub.com/gorogoa-wants-to-get-you-thinking-about-much-more-than-1821949817 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 开发 ==
[[File:Jason_roberts_gdc_2018_cropped.jpg|thumb]]]]
杰森·罗伯茨全职工作闲暇之余，会看一些互动式漫画。受此启发，他着手开发一款卡牌游戏，但后来认为这种风格太过复杂<ref name="Polygon"/><ref name="Kotaku"/>。他打算写一部图画小说，但后来《[[时空幻境_(2008年游戏)|时空幻境]]》等独立游戏作品大获成功，又让他意识到应该将自己对艺术及互动式电子游戏的爱融合到一起，尽管对此类游戏的开发知之甚少<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.polygon.com/features/2017/1/27/14400800/gorogoa-preview|title=The ineffable loveliness of Gorogoa|last=Campbell|first=Colin|date=2017-01-27|work=Polygon|access-date=2017-01-27|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030307/http://www.polygon.com/features/2017/1/27/14400800/gorogoa-preview|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏的开发工作于2011年正式开始，罗伯茨辞去全职工作，潜心投入游戏<ref name=":3" /><ref name="igf">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/211040/Road_to_the_IGF_Jason_Roberts_Gorogoa.php|title=Road to the IGF: Jason Roberts' Gorogoa|last=Graft|first=Kris|date=2014-02-18|work=Gamasutra|accessdate=2014-03-01|archive-date=2020-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303112529/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/211040/Road_to_the_IGF_Jason_Roberts_Gorogoa.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏原定于2013年发行，此时罗伯茨历经两年的开发工程已经花光全部积蓄，幸得{{le|独立基金会|Indie Fund}}的投资，才将开发工作又延长了一年。后来在2016年12月，[[Annapurna_Pictures|安纳布尔纳影业]]宣布成立[[安纳布尔纳互动|安纳布尔纳互动]]品牌，专注游戏发行，《画中世界》成为该品牌首批发行作品之一<ref name=":3" /><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.engadget.com/2016/12/01/movie-studio-annapurna-pictures-now-makes-games/|title=Movie studio Annapurna Pictures now makes games|last=Regan|first=Tom|date=2016-12-01|work=Engadget|accessdate=2016-12-01|archive-date=2016-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204121206/https://www.engadget.com/2016/12/01/movie-studio-annapurna-pictures-now-makes-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

罗伯茨以“Gorogoa”（画中世界）作为游戏的名称，这是他孩提时代虚构的一种生物。他表示，之所以把它当作游戏名称，是因为游戏本身没有文字，任何人都能游玩，不管哪种语言，也因为如此他没有在游戏中加入任何文字语言<ref name="Kotaku" /><ref name="EuroG" />。

游戏起初由罗伯茨在[[Java|Java]]平台上利用定制[[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]编写，但最终被Wholesale Algorithms移植到[[Unity_(游戏引擎)|Unity]]引擎<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.reddit.com/r/NintendoSwitch/comments/7kuy5i/official_ama_with_jason_roberts_the_developer_of/drhevqa/.compact |title=Official AMA with Jason Roberts, the developer of Gorogoa!}}</ref>，方便在[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]等平台上发行作品。游戏中的所有插画都由罗伯茨绘制<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/10/11/gorogoa-indie-surreal-puzzler/ |title= Gorogoa is a completely hand-drawn puzzler of Magritte-esque surrealism |date= 2012-10-11 |accessdate= 2014-01-02 |first= Omri |last= Petitte |work= PC Gamer |archive-date= 2013-11-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131103004203/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/10/11/gorogoa-indie-surreal-puzzler/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，他表示自己的美术风格受{{le|大卫·罗伯茨|David Roberts (painter)}}、[[古斯塔夫·多雷|古斯塔夫·多雷]]、{{le|克里斯托弗·曼森|Christopher Manson}}和{{le|克里斯·韦尔|Chris Ware}}影响<ref name="igf" />。由于他曾到过[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]等地旅游，画作也受[[拜占庭艺术|拜占庭艺术]]的间接影响。他表示，在三维空间中探索二维艺术作品是他创作谜题时的难点。另外，这种绘画风格也让游戏的世界有现实历史元素的意味<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2017/12/on-the-byzantine-art-of-gorogoa.html | title = On the Byzantine Art of Gorogoa | first = Holly | last = Green | date = 2017-12-27 | accessdate = 2018-11-07 | work = Paste | archive-date = 2020-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200303112523/https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2017/12/on-the-byzantine-art-of-gorogoa.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏的音频在开发工作的前几年一直由奥斯丁·温托里（Austin Wintory）创作，但罗伯茨后来想要不同的风格，于是聘请为2012年游戏《{{tsl|en|The Unfinished Swan|未完成的天鹅}}》谱曲的{{le|乔尔·科立兹|Joel Corelitz}}创作。爱德华多·奥尔蒂斯·法劳（Eduardo Ortiz Frau）担任音效设计<ref name="PCG">{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/previews/gorogoa-first-look-a-charming-and-beautiful-illustrative-puzzle-game/|title=Gorogoa first look: a charming and beautiful illustrative puzzle game|last=Warr|first=Philippa|date=2013-12-23|accessdate=2014-01-02|work=PC Gamer|archive-date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140805063450/http://www.pcgamer.com/previews/gorogoa-first-look-a-charming-and-beautiful-illustrative-puzzle-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏配乐由玩家当前关卡中的音频构成<ref name=":3" />。

游戏于2012年{{le|IndieCade|IndieCade}}公布，演示版不久后发布，完整版于2017年12月公开<ref name="PCG" /><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.adventuregamers.com/news/view/22995 |title= Demo for Gorogoa opens window into unique new puzzler |date= 2012-10-11 |accessdate= 2014-01-02 |first= Jack |last= Allin |work= Adventure Gamers |archive-date= 2020-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200303112540/https://adventuregamers.com/news/view/22995 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2017/12/04/long-awaited-indie-gorogoa-arrives-on-ios-and-pc-december-14th/|title=Long-awaited indie ‘Gorogoa’ arrives on iOS and PC December 14th|last=Lumb|first=David|date=2017-12-04|website=Engadget|access-date=2017-12-14|archive-date=2019-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804073953/http://www.engadget.com/2017/12/04/long-awaited-indie-gorogoa-arrives-on-ios-and-pc-december-14th/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。罗伯茨表示，由于自己的画画能力不断提高，需要不断重新绘画前期的场景，游戏的开发周期比预期长了许多<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/03/11/igf-factor-2014-gorogoa/|title=IGF Factor 2014: Gorogoa|last=Walker|first=John|date=2014-03-11|work=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|accessdate=2014-03-21|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123225500/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/03/11/igf-factor-2014-gorogoa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。开发过程中，他还数次推倒重画游戏中的大部分内容<ref name=":3" />。

